      <title>爱沙尼亚科技领袖联手在乌克兰建立反无人机系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/estonia-tech-chiefs-unite-to-build-anti-drone-systems-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家新成立的爱沙尼亚国防公司宣布，将开始在乌克兰生产反无人机导弹系统，而目前这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家正面临俄罗斯日益猛烈的空袭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/estonia-tech-chiefs-unite-to-build-anti-drone-systems-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:42:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国承诺抗击非洲痘病毒，直至疫情得到控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/us-committed-to-combat-african-mpox-until-outbreak-under-control</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国将继续与非洲疾病控制与预防中心以及世界卫生组织合作，确保非洲致命的猪瘟疫情不会发展成为一场大流行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/us-committed-to-combat-african-mpox-until-outbreak-under-control</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:36:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党参议员呼吁美联储降息 75 个基点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/democratic-senators-call-on-fed-to-cut-rates-by-75-basis-points</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三名民主党参议员敦促美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔和其他政策制定者大幅下调央行基准利率，包括本周下调 75 个基点，以保护美国经济免受潜在损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/democratic-senators-call-on-fed-to-cut-rates-by-75-basis-points</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 13:50:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚当斯事件频发，纽约市前消防官员被指控受贿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/two-former-nyc-fire-officials-charged-in-federal-bribery-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着联邦调查继续席卷纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯的政府，两名前纽约消防局官员被指控受贿和腐败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/two-former-nyc-fire-officials-charged-in-federal-bribery-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 13:47:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政变幸存者阿尔塞规划摆脱玻利维亚金融危机之路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/coup-survivor-arce-charts-exit-from-bolivia-s-financial-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玻利维亚总统路易斯·阿尔塞誓言将优先考虑燃料进口和债务偿还，以解决美元短缺问题，避免这个安第斯国家陷入混乱的边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/coup-survivor-arce-charts-exit-from-bolivia-s-financial-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国探索提高低收入者和女性的养老金储蓄</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/uk-explores-boosting-pension-saving-by-low-earners-and-women</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新的研究表明，许多人没有为老年储蓄足够的钱，英国正在考虑增加低收入者和女性的退休储蓄的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/uk-explores-boosting-pension-saving-by-low-earners-and-women</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 12:55:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚央行行长抨击国际货币基金组织与俄罗斯重新接触的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/estonia-s-central-bank-chief-slams-imf-plan-to-re-engage-with-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚央行行长与一些欧洲财政部长一道，批评国际货币基金组织自俄罗斯入侵乌克兰以来首次重启对俄罗斯经济的审查计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/estonia-s-central-bank-chief-slams-imf-plan-to-re-engage-with-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 12:50:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西非数百万人受洪水影响后将迎来更多降雨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/west-africa-braces-for-more-rain-after-floods-displace-millions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西非本周将迎来更多暴雨，该地区发生洪灾，仅 2024 年一年就有至少 230 万人因水位上涨而流离失所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/west-africa-braces-for-more-rain-after-floods-displace-millions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 10:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德聘请卡玛拉·哈里斯顾问派尔担任高级职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/blackrock-brings-back-kamala-harris-adviser-pyle-in-senior-role</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司 (BlackRock Inc.) 正在重新聘用曾任卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 高级助理、该公司高管的迈克·派尔 (Mike Pyle)，此举将加强这家全球最大资产管理公司与华盛顿之间的密切联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/blackrock-brings-back-kamala-harris-adviser-pyle-in-senior-role</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普高尔夫俱乐部枪击事件是 2024 年大选的最新冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/gunfire-at-trump-golf-club-latest-jolt-in-chaotic-2024-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国现代政治史上最混乱的总统竞选活动之一周日再次出现戏剧性转折，一名据称刺客出现在前总统唐纳德·特朗普身边，引发了在其佛罗里达高尔夫俱乐部发生的枪战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/gunfire-at-trump-golf-club-latest-jolt-in-chaotic-2024-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 00:13:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
